16.2 Compensation
:SKRSLUT.
.br
16.2.1 The insurance covers fire damage to, burglary, open theft and
robbery of personal effects brought on the journey up to a sum of DKK
30,000, with an excess of DKK 1,000 per insurance event. Items
belonging to the insured's employer are also covered within this
insurance sum. Payment of compensation is conditional upon burglary, open
theft and robbery of baggage or hard currency being reported to
the nearest police authority. A receipt for this report is to be
enclosed with the claim report.
.sp 3mm
.kp off
.kp on
The maximum compensation for the following shall be limited to DKK
6,000 in the event of fire, burglary, open theft or robbery:
.of 5mm
*¤hard currency
.of
.kp off
.kp on
.of 5mm
*¤travellers' cheques, fuel and restaurant
vouchers, tickets, passports, ski-lift passes and green fees.
.of
.kp off
.kp on
.of 5mm
*¤Items that fully or partially consists of precious metals, genuine
pearls and gemstones, antiques, works of art, hand-knotted
carpets/rugs, pocket watches and wristwatches, furs and
fur items, binoculars, musical instruments, CDs, computer disks
and accessories for the items mentioned here, weapons and accessories
for same ammunition, wines and spirits.
.of
