16.6 Reporting claims
:SKRSLUT.
.br
On returning home, a claim report is to be submitted to Privatsikring
together with documentation for the lost items.
.sp 3mm
.kp off
.kp on
With regard to the loss of all baggage, theft of items from baggage or
damage to baggage, refer to the regulations concerning checked baggage
published on the individual airline's websites. Please note that the
airlines have specific regulations concerning what may be packed in
checked luggage with regard to valuables, electronic equipment, foods
and the like.
.br
The PIR report from the airline must be submitted together with the claim.
.sp 3mm
.kp off
.kp on
If theft, loss or damage to baggage is discovered subsequent to arrival
at the destination or return home, the airline/airport is to be
contacted with a view to requesting confirmation that the grounds for
the claim arose while the baggage was in the possession of the airline.
*¤theft from unlocked motor vehicles, caravans, pleasure craft or tents
.of
.kp off
.kp on
.of 5mm
*¤damage attributable to inappropriate packing and standard treatment
of suitcases and other baggage
.of
.kp off
.kp on
.of 5mm
*¤theft from or damage to the insured's checked baggage, where the
items are covered by the airline regulations concerning items that
are not to be checked. Generally speaking, airlines accept no
liability whatsoever if the insured checks personal effects
including money, keys, medicine, glasses/sunglasses, jewellery, pearls
and precious metals, computers and other personal electronic
equipment, mobile phones, musical instruments, securities, passports
and other identification documents, or damage to or caused by
foods, bottles, glass and similar items packed in the baggage. The
insured should contact the individual airline for
additional information concerning checked baggage.
.of
.kp off
.kp on
.of 5mm
*¤theft of baggage left without adequate supervision. The insured
must not leave baggage unattended - not even for a short time - unless
it is locked in a building, motor vehicle, left luggage locker or similar.
