16.4 Obligations
:SKRSLUT.
.br
The insured is to show care and attention with regard to the handling
and storage of the insured items. The insured is additionally obliged
to familiarise himself/herself with the regulations concerning
checked baggage. This information is published online on the
respective airlines' websites.
.sp 3mm
.kp off
.kp on
In the event of theft or robbery, a report must be filed with the
nearest police authority without delay.
