16.2.2 In the event of the loss of all baggage, theft from baggage
or damage to checked baggage, the claim report is to be accompanied
by a report from the airline on the loss/damage/theft.
.sp 3mm
.kp off
.kp on
16.2.3 Compensation of up to DKK 6,000 per claim is payable for the theft
of luggage from locked motor vehicles, on condition that said luggage has
been placed in a boot or glove compartment that is locked and separated
from the main vehicle cabin, and where the contents are not visible from
outside.
